Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Title,,0,0,0,,SKIP THE CLEANUP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Painting or sanding?\NSkip hours of cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:08.00,Title,,0,0,0,,TAPE + FILM IN ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:08.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Pre-taped masking film combines yellow tape\Nand clear PE film in one roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Title,,0,0,0,,TAPE FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,First, press the yellow tape firmly\Nalong the cabinet edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Title,,0,0,0,,PULL DOWN TO COVER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Then pull the film down smoothly\Nto cover the tile and countertop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.20,Title,,0,0,0,,TEAR BY HAND
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Fix the far edge, pull tight, and tear it by hand.\NNo scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.40,Title,,0,0,0,,PAINT STAYS ON FILM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.40,Caption,,0,0,0,,Paint and dust stay on the film,\Nnot on your furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.80,Title,,0,0,0,,PEEL CLEAN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.80,Caption,,0,0,0,,Peel it away. No damage, no sticky residue,\Nand no cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:35.80,Title,,0,0,0,,FASTER MASKING. LESS CLEANUP.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:35.80,Caption,,0,0,0,,One roll, faster masking, and far less cleanup.\NTry pre-taped masking film on your next project.

